 <div class="fg"><label class="fl"> 项目网站</label><input class="fi" id="lk-web" placeholder="https://yourproject.xyz"></div>
 <div class="fg"><label class="fl">🐦 Twitter / X</label><input class="fi" id="lk-twitter" placeholder="https://x.com/yourproject"></div>
 </div>
 <div class="fr2" style="margin-bottom:4px">
 <div class="fg"><label class="fl">✈️ Telegram</label><input class="fi" id="lk-tg" placeholder="https://t.me/yourgroup"></div>
 
 </div>

 <div class="fr2">
 <div class="fg"><label class="fl">分类</label><select class="fs" id="lk-label"><option value="Meme">🐸 Meme</option><option value="AI"> AI</option><option value="Defi"> Defi</option><option value="Games">🎮 Games</option><option value="Social">💬 Social</option><option value="Others"> Others</option></select></div>
 <div class="fg"><label class="fl">Logo</label><div class="lh-upload" onclick="document.getElementById('lk-file').click()" id="lh-upload-area"><input type="file" id="lk-file" accept="image/*" style="display:none" onchange="onLogoUpload(this)"><div id="lh-upload-icon">📷</div><div id="lh-upload-tip">点击上传<br><span style="font-size:10px">jpg/png/webp</span></div></div></div>
 </div>
 </div>
 <div class="card-flat">
 <div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:20px;padding-bottom:14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--bd)"> Agent 激励设置</div>
 <div class="fg"><label class="fl">交易税率（税收→taxPool 合约）</label>
 <div class="lh-tax-grid">
 <label class="lh-tax-opt"><input type="radio" name="tax" value="" checked onchange="updateTaxFlow(this.value)"><span>无税</span></label>
 <label class="lh-tax-opt"><input type="radio" name="tax" value="1" onchange="updateTaxFlow(this.value)"><span>1%</span></label>
 <label class="lh-tax-opt lh-tax-rec"><input type="radio" name="tax" value="3" onchange="updateTaxFlow(this.value)"><span>3% 推荐</span></label>
 <label class="lh-tax-opt"><input type="radio" name="tax" value="5" onchange="updateTaxFlow(this.value)"><span>5%</span></label>
 </div>
 </div>
 <!-- 税收→Agent 运营说明 -->
 <div style="padding:14px;background:rgba(124,58,237,.06);border:1px solid rgba(124,58,237,.15);border-radius:12px;margin-bottom:4px">
 <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;color:var(--p)">🔄 税收自动驱动 Agent 运营</div>
 <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px" id="tax-flow-desc">
 <div class="empty" style="font-size:12px;color:var(--tx3)">← 先选择税率</div>
 </div>
 </div>

 <div id="launch-quota" style="text-align:center;font-size:11px;color:var(--tx3);margin-bottom:8px">连接钱包后显示剩余发币次数</div>
 <button class="btnp" style="width:100%;padding:14px;font-size:15px;font-weight:700" onclick="launchToken()" id="launch-btn"> 立即发币</button>
 <div id="launch-error" style="display:none;padding:10px 14px;background:rgba(239,68,68,.08);border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.2);border-radius:10px;font-size:12px;color:#f87171;margin-top:10px"></div>
 <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--tx3);text-align:center;margin-top:10px;line-height:1.7"> 为防止恶意发币，平台对 API 请求有频率限制<br>若提示「请稍后重试」，等待 1-2 分钟即可</div>
 
 <p style="font-size:11px;color:var(--tx3);text-align:center;margin-top:8px">发币 Gas 由你的钱包支付 · 税收 100% 进入 taxPool 合约，Agent 自动提取运营</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>
 <div class="lh-progress" id="launch-progress" style="display:none"><div class="lh-progress-inner"><div class="ai-spinner" style="width:40px;height:40px;border-width:3px"></div><div id="lp-msg" style="font-size:14px;color:var(--tx2);margin-top:16px">准备中...</div><div id="lp-steps" style="width:100%;max-width:380px;margin-top:20px"></div></div></div>
 <div class="lh-result" id="launch-result" style="display:none"><div class="lh-result-inner">
 <div style="font-size:48px;margin-bottom:16px"></div>
 <div class="lh-result-title">发币成功！</div>
 <div id="lr-task" style="font-size:13px;color:var(--tx2);margin-top:8px;margin-bottom:16px"></div>
 <!-- 代币地址卡片 -->
 <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-radius:12px;padding:14px 16px;margin-bottom:16px">
 <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(--tx3);margin-bottom:6px">代币合约地址</div>
 <div id="lr-addr" style="font-size:12px;font-family:monospace;color:var(--p);word-break:break-all;line-height:1.6"></div>
 <button class="btns" style="font-size:11px;padding:4px 10px;margin-top:8px" onclick="navigator.clipboard?.writeText(document.getElementById('lr-addr').textContent).then(()=>toast('地址已复制','s'))">复制地址</button>
 </div>
 <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;margin-bottom:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center">
 <a id="lr-scan" href="#" target="_blank" class="btns" style="text-decoration:none">◈ BSCScan ↗</a>
 <a id="lr-fourmeme" href="#" target="_blank" class="btnp" style="text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;padding:10px 20px">🛒 去 Four.meme 买入 ↗</a>
 <button class="btns" onclick="G('my',document.querySelectorAll('.nl')[5]||document.querySelector('.nl:last-child'))"> 我的记录</button>
 </div>
 <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--tx3);margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.6"> 税收已自动接入 Agent，无需额外操作<br> 可选：充值预算委托 Agent 加速运营</div>
 <button class="btns" style="width:100%;padding:12px;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:10px" onclick="showInlineDelegate()"> 加速委托（可选）→</button>
 <button class="btns" style="width:100%" onclick="resetLaunch()">再发一个代币</button>

 <!-- 内联委托区（发币后展开）-->
 <div id="inline-delegate" style="display:none;margin-top:20px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);padding-top:20px;text-align:left">
 <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:var(--tx);margin-bottom:16px">选择 Agent 类型</div>
 <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px;margin-bottom:16px">
 <div onclick="dgSelectAgent('hunter');this.parentNode.querySelectorAll('[data-ag]').forEach(e=>e.style.borderColor='rgba(255,255,255,.1)');this.style.borderColor='rgba(124,58,237,.6)'" data-ag="hunter" style="padding:12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-radius:12px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s">
 <div style="font-size:16px">🔴</div><div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--tx);margin-top:4px">猎手</div><div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--tx3)">激进拉新</div>
 </div>
 <div onclick="dgSelectAgent('strategist');this.parentNode.querySelectorAll('[data-ag]').forEach(e=>e.style.borderColor='rgba(255,255,255,.1)');this.style.borderColor='rgba(124,58,237,.6)'" data-ag="strategist" style="padding:12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-radius:12px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s">
 <div style="font-size:16px">🟡</div><div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--tx);margin-top:4px">军师</div><div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--tx3)">数据驱动</div>
 </div>
 <div onclick="dgSelectAgent('herald');this.parentNode.querySelectorAll('[data-ag]').forEach(e=>e.style.borderColor='rgba(255,255,255,.1)');this.style.borderColor='rgba(124,58,237,.6)'" data-ag="herald" style="padding:12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-radius:12px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s">
 <div style="font-size:16px">🟢</div><div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--tx);margin-top:4px">传令官</div><div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--tx3)">故事叙事</div>
 </div>
 <div onclick="dgSelectAgent('custom');this.parentNode.querySelectorAll('[data-ag]').forEach(e=>e.style.borderColor='rgba(255,255,255,.1)');this.style.borderColor='rgba(124,58,237,.6)'" data-ag="custom" style="padding:12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-radius:12px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s">
 <div style="font-size:16px"></div><div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--tx);margin-top:4px">自定义</div><div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--tx3)">完全掌控</div>
 </div>
 </div>
 <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px;margin-bottom:12px">
 <div><label style="font-size:11px;color:var(--tx3);display:block;margin-bottom:4px">预算 BNB *</label><input class="fi" id="id1" type="number" placeholder="0.05" min="0.01" step="0.01"></div>
 <div><label style="font-size:11px;color:var(--tx3);display:block;margin-bottom:4px">运营时长（分钟）</label><input class="fi" id="id2" type="number" value="120" min="10"></div>
 </div>
 <button class="btnp" style="width:100%;padding:13px;font-size:14px" id="inline-dg-btn" onclick="submitInlineDelegate()"> 确认委托（需签名2次）</button>
 <div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--tx3);text-align:center;margin-top:8px">资金托管合约 · 到期随时退款</div>
 </div>

 </div></div>
</div>

<div id="page-how" class="pw" style="display:none">

 <!-- S1: 大字幕 -->
 <div class="how-hero">
 <div class="how-label">◆ &nbsp;PROTOCOL ARCHITECTURE</div>
 <h2 class="how-title">ERC-8183<br><span class="gd">AI Agent Protocol</span></h2>
 <p class="how-sub">ODA 三层架构 · 链上透明 · 自主决策 · 零人工干预</p>
 </div>

 <!-- S2: 六步流程 大字竖排 -->
 <div class="how-steps">
 <div class="hs-line"></div>
 <div class="hs-item" style="--d:0s">
 <div class="hs-num">01</div>
 <div class="hs-dot"></div>
 <div class="hs-body">
 <div class="hs-tag">ON-CHAIN DELEGATION</div>
 <div class="hs-title">项目方发起链上委托</div>
 <div class="hs-desc">任何人都可以成为任务发布者。项目方在网页填写目标代币、激励目标、管理周期，充值 BNB 预算——三笔交易完成链上委托。资金由 ERC-8183 智能合约托管，连平台都无法挪用。</div>
 <div class="hs-pill">ERC-8183 托管 · 随时可退款</div>
 </div>
 </div>
 <div class="hs-item rev" style="--d:.1s">
 <div class="hs-num">02</div>
 <div class="hs-dot"></div>
 <div class="hs-body">
 <div class="hs-tag">AI OBSERVATION</div>
 <div class="hs-title">Agent 观察链上</div>
 <div class="hs-desc">Agent 每 30 分钟扫描一次链上数据：谁在买、谁在卖、持仓时长分布、新地址增速、交易量趋势。数据不说谎，Agent 用数据做决定，不靠感觉。</div>
 <div class="hs-pill">链上数据 · 实时分析</div>
 </div>
 </div>
 <div class="hs-item" style="--d:.2s">
 <div class="hs-num">03</div>
 <div class="hs-dot"></div>
 <div class="hs-body">
 <div class="hs-tag">LLM DECISION</div>
 <div class="hs-title">LLM 生成任务策略</div>
 <div class="hs-desc">将链上状态喂给大语言模型，输出结构化决策：发什么类型的任务？奖励多少 BNB？面向哪类持有者？取消哪些没人做的任务？每一步都有理由，日志可查。</div>
 <div class="hs-pill">GPT-4o · JSON 决策输出</div>
 </div>
 </div>
 <div class="hs-item rev" style="--d:.3s">
 <div class="hs-num">04</div>
 <div class="hs-dot"></div>
 <div class="hs-body">
 <div class="hs-tag">ON-CHAIN EXECUTION</div>
 <div class="hs-title">自动上链发布任务</div>
 <div class="hs-desc">Agent 直接调用智能合约 createTask()，将奖励 BNB/MBT 质押在合约中。没有人工审批，没有中间人，资金始终锁在链上——连 Agent 自己都拿不走。</div>
 <div class="hs-pill">智能合约质押 · 不可篡改</div>
 </div>
 </div>
 <div class="hs-item" style="--d:.4s">
 <div class="hs-num">05</div>
 <div class="hs-dot"></div>
 <div class="hs-body">
 <div class="hs-tag">CHAIN VERIFICATION</div>
 <div class="hs-title">链上自动核查行为</div>
 <div class="hs-desc">五种验证方式全部在链上完成：持仓时长（区块时间戳）、买入金额（交易事件）、早鸟顺序（先来先得）、推荐关系（链上注册）、锦标赛排名（截止时快照）。不需要信任任何人。</div>
 <div class="hs-pill">5 种链上验证 · 零人工</div>
 </div>
 </div>
 <div class="hs-item rev" style="--d:.5s">
 <div class="hs-num">06</div>
 <div class="hs-dot"></div>
 <div class="hs-body">
 <div class="hs-tag">AUTO REWARD</div>
 <div class="hs-title">奖励即时到账</div>
 <div class="hs-desc">验证通过，合约即时转账——BNB 或任意代币精准流向完成任务的用户。没有提现申请，没有人工审核，没有等待期。奖励实时到账，任务完成率越高，委托方意愿越强，飞轮持续加速。</div>
 <div class="hs-pill">秒级到账 · 飞轮加速</div>
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>

 <!-- S3: 双模式对比 -->
 <div class="how-modes">
 <div class="hm-label">◆ &nbsp;两种运行模式</div>
 <div class="hm-grid">
 <div class="hm-card hm-mbt">
 <div class="hm-head">
 <div class="hm-icon">🔄</div>
 <div>
