 <div class="hm-arrow">↓ 完成领奖</div>
 <div class="hm-node hm-node-hl">持有者获得 MBT 奖励</div>
 <div class="hm-arrow">↓ 持仓增加</div>
 <div class="hm-node">更多交易 → 更多税收</div>
 </div>
