 <div class="hm-arrow">↓ 自主决策</div>
 <div class="hm-node">针对该代币发布任务</div>
 <div class="hm-arrow">↓ 持续汇报</div>
 <div class="hm-node hm-node-hl">社区活跃度提升</div>
