 <div class="hg-stat"><div class="hg-snum">5</div><div class="hg-slbl">验证类型</div></div>
 <div class="hg-stat"><div class="hg-snum">∞</div><div class="hg-slbl">可用奖励币种</div></div>
 </div>
 </div>

</div>

 



<div id="page-fair" class="pw" style="display:none">
  <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 28px 100px">
    <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:40px;flex-wrap:wrap">
      <button id="fair-page-security" onclick="fairTab('security',this)" style="padding:8px 20px;border-radius:20px;border:1px solid var(--p);background:rgba(124,58,237,.15);color:var(--p);font-size:13px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer"> 公平保障</button>
      
    </div>
    <div id="fair-section-security">
<div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:60px 28px 100px">

<!-- HERO -->
<div style="margin-bottom:64px">
  <div class="label" style="margin-bottom:16px">◆ &nbsp;SEKI FAIR PROTOCOL</div>
  <h2 class="display" style="margin-bottom:20px">公平保障<br><span class="accent">代码即规则</span></h2>
  <p style="font-size:16px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.9;max-width:600px">Seki 的每一笔委托资金由链上合约自动托管。无需信任平台，无需信任 Agent——信任代码就够了。</p>
</div>

<!-- 核心原则 3列 -->
<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:16px;margin-bottom:64px">
  <div style="padding:28px;background:rgba(124,58,237,.06);border:1px solid rgba(124,58,237,.2);border-radius:20px">
    <div style="width:36px;height:36px;background:rgba(124,58,237,.2);border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:18px;margin-bottom:16px">⛓</div>
    <div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:8px;letter-spacing:-.3px">资金链上托管</div>
    <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.8">委托预算直接锁入 AgentRegistry 合约。平台服务器、Agent 钱包、任何第三方都无法直接提取。资金只能由合约规则触发流动，地址公开可链上验证。</div>
  </div>
  <div style="padding:28px;background:rgba(52,211,153,.05);border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,.18);border-radius:20px">
    <div style="width:36px;height:36px;background:rgba(52,211,153,.15);border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:18px;margin-bottom:16px">🔑</div>
    <div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:8px;letter-spacing:-.3px">私钥完全隔离</div>
    <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.8">Agent 运营钱包只用于支付 Gas（每次约 0.002 BNB），不持有任何委托资金。即使私钥泄露，攻击者也无法动用项目方资金。</div>
  </div>
  <div style="padding:28px;background:rgba(96,165,250,.05);border:1px solid rgba(96,165,250,.18);border-radius:20px">
    <div style="width:36px;height:36px;background:rgba(96,165,250,.15);border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:18px;margin-bottom:16px">↩</div>
    <div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:8px;letter-spacing:-.3px">随时全额退款</div>
    <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.8">委托到期后任何人可调用 claimRefund()，合约自动将剩余 BNB 全额退回项目方钱包。无需平台审批，代码自动执行。即使平台关闭，退款功能依然有效。</div>
  </div>
  <div style="padding:28px;background:rgba(245,158,11,.05);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.18);border-radius:20px">
    <div style="width:36px;height:36px;background:rgba(245,158,11,.15);border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:18px;margin-bottom:16px">◈</div>
    <div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:8px;letter-spacing:-.3px">持仓门槛验证</div>
    <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.8">链上验证用户持有目标代币达到门槛才可领取奖励。合约自动查余额，防止女巫攻击，保障真实持仓者权益。</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ERC-8183 状态机 -->
<div style="margin-bottom:64px">
  <div class="label" style="margin-bottom:16px">◆ &nbsp;ERC-8183 委托生命周期</div>
  <h3 style="font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,32px);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-1px;margin-bottom:8px">Job 状态机</h3>
  <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:36px">Seki 完整实现 ERC-8183 Agentic Commerce Protocol（<a href="https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-8183" target="_blank" style="color:var(--p);font-weight:700">原文标准 ↗</a>）。每笔委托都是一个四状态链上 Job：<strong style="color:var(--tx)">Client</strong>（代币发行者）出资 → <strong style="color:var(--tx)">Provider</strong>（持币用户）完成任务 → <strong style="color:var(--tx)">Evaluator</strong>（Seki ExecutorAgent）链上验收 → 合约自动打款。每个状态转移由合约强制执行，不可篡改，不可绕过。</p>

  <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0;align-items:stretch;margin-bottom:24px">
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:140px;padding:20px 16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);border-radius:16px 0 0 16px;text-align:center">
      <div style="width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:#6b7280;margin:0 auto 10px"></div>
      <div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:800;color:#9ca3af;letter-spacing:.5px;margin-bottom:6px">OPEN</div>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--tx3);line-height:1.6">委托已创建<br>资金未锁定</div>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 4px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.2);font-size:18px">→</div>
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:140px;padding:20px 16px;background:rgba(96,165,250,.06);border:1px solid rgba(96,165,250,.2);text-align:center">
      <div style="width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:#60a5fa;margin:0 auto 10px"></div>
      <div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:800;color:#60a5fa;letter-spacing:.5px;margin-bottom:6px">FUNDED</div>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--tx3);line-height:1.6">BNB 锁入<br>合约托管</div>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 4px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.2);font-size:18px">→</div>
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:140px;padding:20px 16px;background:rgba(245,158,11,.06);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.2);text-align:center">
      <div style="width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:#f59e0b;margin:0 auto 10px"></div>
      <div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:800;color:#f59e0b;letter-spacing:.5px;margin-bottom:6px">SUBMITTED</div>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--tx3);line-height:1.6">Agent 提交<br>工作报告</div>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 4px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.2);font-size:18px">→</div>
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:140px;padding:20px 16px;background:rgba(52,211,153,.06);border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,.2);border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;text-align:center">
      <div style="width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:#34d399;margin:0 auto 10px"></div>
      <div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:800;color:#34d399;letter-spacing:.5px;margin-bottom:6px">COMPLETED</div>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--tx3);line-height:1.6">项目方确认<br>资金划拨</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 退出路径 -->
  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px">
    <div style="padding:16px 20px;background:rgba(239,68,68,.05);border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.15);border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px">
      <div style="width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#ef4444;flex-shrink:0"></div>
      <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.6">项目方不满意 → <span style="color:#f87171;font-weight:700">Rejected</span> → 全额退款至项目方钱包</div>
    </div>
    <div style="padding:16px 20px;background:rgba(239,68,68,.05);border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.15);border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px">
      <div style="width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#f59e0b;flex-shrink:0"></div>
      <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.6">超过截止时间 → <span style="color:#fbbf24;font-weight:700">Expired</span> → 任何人可触发自动退款</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- V1 vs V2 对比 -->
<div style="margin-bottom:64px">
  <div class="label" style="margin-bottom:16px">◆ &nbsp;SECURITY UPGRADE</div>
  <h3 style="font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,32px);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-1px;margin-bottom:8px">V2 彻底改变了资金托管方式</h3>
  <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:32px">在 V1 架构里，Agent 钱包直接持有项目方的委托资金——私钥等于资金控制权。一旦私钥泄露，所有资金面临风险。V2 从根本上改变了这一设计：委托资金全程由链上合约锁定，Agent 仅在执行任务时消耗少量 Gas，永远不持有委托预算。</p>
  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px">
    <div style="padding:24px;background:rgba(239,68,68,.05);border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.18);border-radius:16px">
      <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1.5px;color:#f87171;margin-bottom:20px">✗ V1 旧设计</div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;margin-bottom:16px">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap">
          <span style="font-size:11px;padding:4px 10px;background:rgba(239,68,68,.1);border-radius:6px;color:#fca5a5">项目方 BNB</span>
          <span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.25)">→</span>
          <span style="font-size:11px;padding:4px 10px;background:rgba(239,68,68,.2);border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.4);border-radius:6px;color:#f87171;font-weight:700">Agent 私人钱包</span>
          <span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.25)">→</span>
          <span style="font-size:11px;padding:4px 10px;background:rgba(239,68,68,.1);border-radius:6px;color:#fca5a5">任务奖池</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:12px;background:rgba(239,68,68,.07);border-radius:8px;font-size:12px;color:#f87171;line-height:1.7">
        Agent 私钥 = 完全控制权<br>私钥一旦泄露，项目方资金可被直接转走
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="padding:24px;background:rgba(52,211,153,.05);border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,.18);border-radius:16px">
      <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1.5px;color:#34d399;margin-bottom:20px">✓ V2 当前设计</div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;margin-bottom:16px">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap">
          <span style="font-size:11px;padding:4px 10px;background:rgba(52,211,153,.08);border-radius:6px;color:#6ee7b7">项目方 BNB</span>
          <span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.25)">→</span>
          <span style="font-size:11px;padding:4px 10px;background:rgba(52,211,153,.15);border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,.3);border-radius:6px;color:#34d399;font-weight:700">合约锁定</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap">
          <span style="font-size:11px;padding:4px 10px;background:rgba(52,211,153,.06);border-radius:6px;color:#6ee7b7">Agent（仅 Gas）</span>
          <span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.25)">→</span>
          <span style="font-size:11px;padding:4px 10px;background:rgba(52,211,153,.06);border-radius:6px;color:#6ee7b7">合约划拨奖励</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:12px;background:rgba(52,211,153,.06);border-radius:8px;font-size:12px;color:#34d399;line-height:1.7">
        Agent 私钥泄露 = 最多损失几分钱 Gas<br>项目方资金在合约里，Agent 无法直接动用
      </div>
    </div>
