            <div><div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px">配置 .env</div><div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--tx3)">填写合约地址、Agent 钱包私钥、RPC URL、LLM API Key（支持任意 OpenAI 兼容接口）</div></div>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:16px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start">
            <div style="width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(52,211,153,.2);color:#34d399;font-size:11px;font-weight:900;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0">3</div>
            <div><div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px">启动后端</div><div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--tx3)">npm install && node server.js（端口 3000）+ node loop.js（Agent 每 3 分钟自动运行）</div></div>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:16px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start">
            <div style="width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(52,211,153,.2);color:#34d399;font-size:11px;font-weight:900;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0">4</div>
            <div><div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px">发币并委托</div><div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--tx3)">在「发币」页用 MetaMask 发射 meme 代币（BSC: four.meme），然后到「委托」页选择 Agent 类型并注资</div></div>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:16px 20px;display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start">
            <div style="width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(52,211,153,.2);color:#34d399;font-size:11px;font-weight:900;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0">5</div>
            <div><div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px">Agent 自动运行</div><div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--tx3)">3 分钟后 Agent 开始观察市场信号，根据 5 条触发规则自动发布链上任务，用户完成任务可领取奖励</div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 下载 & 链接 -->
      <div style="margin-bottom:40px">
        <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1.5px;color:#34d399;margin-bottom:16px">◆ &nbsp;下载 & 资源</div>
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:12px">
          <a href="/contract" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:16px 20px;background:rgba(52,211,153,.06);border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,.2);border-radius:14px;text-decoration:none;color:var(--tx)">
            <div style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:10px;background:rgba(52,211,153,.15);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:16px;flex-shrink:0">◈</div>
            <div><div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700">MemeBountyV2.sol</div><div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--tx3)">下载主合约源码</div></div>
          </a>
